information: The company HUOBER BREZEL GMBH & CO. ERSTE WÜRTTEMBERGISCHE BREZELFABRIK, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, founded in 1950, which operates in the Import-export - food and agriculture industry. It is based in Erdmannhausen, Germany.
